snippet.title: Wayward Terran Frontier 0.7.0.00 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the upcoming content patch for Wayward Terran Frontier: Zero Falls.

Patch 0.7.0.00 goes live Saturday 12/16/2017 so play it now because for all you know we could have a global thermonuclear war on monday!

http://store.steampowered.com/app/392080/Wayward_Terran_Frontier_Zero_Falls/
